argin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">融入了奥迪在全球最先进的高科技独家技术，又进一步丰富了豪华的配置，并赋予其超强的运动特性，从设计到性能无不体现出其完美品质。其特点是更豪华、更动感、更成熟。更豪华主要体现在</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; list-style-type: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">BOSE</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; list-style-type: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">音响、电视</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; list-style-type: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">/DVD</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; list-style-type: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">上，而且都是世界一流名牌产品。更动感体现在运动座椅、方向盘上；更成熟体现在奥迪</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; list-style-type: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/21px \'microsoft yahei\'; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">A6</span><span style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; 